LEVERAGE your friends birthday to get leads and sales with just a click!!!
Birthday Wisher is a chrome extension for Facebook that helps you to send automated wishes to all your friends who has their birthdays. It also allows you to send automated personal messages to everyone on their birthdays. It also leaves automated messages after their birthday with a custom message if you choose.
